title: Stop Kubernetes Pod for Debugging
tags: _method k8s @zettel
roam-id: fb3756aa-0d5f-4059-8ea4-5a37ce820d93
type: text/markdown

make pod sleep infinitelly after creation. add the follwing as command

``` yaml
containers:
- name: bird-account-checker
    command: ["sh", "-c", "sleep infinity"] # debug
    image: eu.gcr.io/hopi-program/bird-usy/bird-account-checker:1.0.0
```
